|---|---|
| Missing security headers (`helmet`) | **Medium** |
| No rate limiting | **Medium** |
| `X-Powered-By` exposed | **Low** |
| No error handling middleware | **Low** |
| Hardcoded port | **Info** |
| No CORS configuration | **Info** |

